/**
 * Auto-generated migration regression guard for plugin "forms_validation".
 *
 * Generated by elgg-test-writer. Do not edit by hand — re-run the scaffold
 * (bin/scaffold-smoke-tests.sh --target-version=elgg7).
 *
 * TESTS-FIRST CONTRACT
 * --------------------
 * This test asserts that EVERY statically-detectable failure class from
 * skills/elgg-migrate/references/migration-failure-catalog.md is ABSENT for
 * the target major (Elgg 7.x). Run it BEFORE touching any
 * plugin code:
 *
 *   - BEFORE migration → RED   (the un-migrated plugin still trips the classes)
 *   - AFTER  migration → GREEN (every class is fixed)
 *
 * That RED→GREEN transition is the proof the migration actually landed — not a
 * "it still activates" smoke pass, which the catalog shows repeatedly missing
 * page-render and boot fatals.
 *
 * WHY STATIC (no Elgg boot)
 * -------------------------
 * Most catalog classes fatal at class-load or page-render on the target
 * version, so a booted test crashes before it can assert. The signature has to
 * be caught in the source. Mirrors the engine-side detectors
 * (elgg-migrate/bin/scan-frontend-residue.sh, PostMigrationVerifier,
 * removed-functions.json, changed-class-contracts.json) so the guard travels
 * with the plugin and fails its own CI. Keep the embedded maps in lock-step
 * with those files.
 *
 * Runtime confirmation (real activation + route 200s) is the job of the
 * post-migration SmokeTest and the LLM-driven route/render battery. This file
 * is the deterministic, pre-migration RED gate.
 *
 * Catalog classes covered (target-gated):
 *   FC-*x*x removed symbols ...... testNoRemovedSymbols
 *   FC-3x4x-01 forbidden files ... testNoForbiddenBootstrapFiles
 *   FC-2x3x-02 start.php present .. testStartPhpPresentOn3x
 *   FC-3x4x-10 lowercase id ...... testNoCamelCasePluginIdCallsites
 *   FC-3x4x-09 hook/event mixup .. testNoHookEventConfusion
 *   FC-5x6x-03 Seed shape ........ testSeedSubclassShape
 *   FC-5x6x-04 Batch shape ....... testNoRemovedClassContracts / testUpgradeBatchShape
 *   FC-5x6x-01 Hook removed ...... testNoRemovedClassContracts
 *   FC-4x5x-01 add_translation ... testNoLegacyLanguageFiles
 *   FC-ALL-01  unserialize RCE ... testNoUnsafeUnserialize
 *   FC-ALL-05  route:rewrite@init  testNoRouteRewriteAtInit
 *   FC-ALL-06  ::class in manifest  testManifestUsesStringLiterals
 *   bug-007/013 sig-incompat ..... testNoIncompatibleCoreOverrides
 *   FC-6x7x-03 menu ->add() ...... testMenuRegisterReturnsArray
 *   FC-6x7x-05 css orphaned ...... testNoOrphanedCssElementViews
 */
